          "style_family": null,
          "text": "固请勿疑，啊呀端居相待！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（解三酲） 夫人城倾城怎遇？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "女王国倾国也难模。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拜辞你个画眉京兆府。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那花没艳，酒无娱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忘不了小玉窗前自叹吁。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前军催迫，请大老爷起程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李益",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "知道了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓得哉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "霍小玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吖！难道一刻也停留不得了么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李益、霍小玉",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！啊呀（妻）（李郎）吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李益 （解三酲） 伤情处，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "香冷唇朱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阿呀老爷，三军亦拉笃催哉㖸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李益",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阿呀妻吓！听笳鼓喧鸣，催我行色匆匆，密意深情，非言所尽。阿呀，只得拜"
        },
        {
          "character": "李益",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "别了呢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李益哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "霍小玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妾身也有一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李益 （鹧鸪天） 掩残啼回送你上七香车，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "𠮾碧玉居。"
        },
        {
          "character": "霍小玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李郎！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鹧鸪天） 但愿你封侯游昼锦，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不妨我啼鸟落花初。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李益",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人请回罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "霍小玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李郎慢行！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李益、霍小玉",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！阿呀（妻）（李郎）吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李益下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "霍小玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "浣纱，和你灞桥一望。"
        },
        {
          "character": "浣纱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人引李益同绕场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李益、霍小玉",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！啊呀（妻）（李郎）吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李益、霍小玉",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "教他关河到处休离剑"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李益、众人同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "霍小玉 （鹧鸪天） 他千骑拥，万人扶，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "富贵英雄美丈夫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "浣纱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "绿杨隔断，望不见了，请郡主回去罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "霍小玉 （鹧鸪天） 驿路逢人数寄书。"
        },
        {
          "character": "浣纱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "车来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（霍小玉、浣纱同下。）"
        }
      ],
